The paper discusses a machine learning algorithm, specifically distributed SGD, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The focus of the paper is on the communication trade-off in distributed computing, which suggests that it could also fall under the categories of distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the convergence of the algorithm, which could place it under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) or information theory (cs.IT).
